Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.06,0:00:09.93,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:12.39,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:15.76,Default,Classmate B,0,0,0,,小和  你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:17.90,Default,Classmate A,0,0,0,,裕太  你搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:19.24,Default,Classmate A,0,0,0,,快向小和道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:23.42,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我头脑一热  就会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:28.37,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,哪怕是鸡毛蒜皮的小事  也会大打出手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:34.01,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,每当如此  老师都会找我妈妈谈话
Comment: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:40.77,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我这样的性格  是个性  还是(疾病,BUG)呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:40.77,RUBY,Yuta,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(1299,980)}BUG
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:40.77,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我这样的性格  是个性  还是疾病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:25.74,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,哦？ 开花了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:27.90,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,啊  须堂医生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:29.71,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,要我买个自动浇水器吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.92,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,每天浇水很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.04,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,才不需要那种东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:36.26,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,我浇的不是水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.50,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,我浇的是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:40.33,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:42.01,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,你是在嘲笑我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:45.01,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不  我觉得你说得很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:49.37,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,医生夸奖我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:51.52,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,那你也来一起浇…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:53.80,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,休息时间已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:56.54,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.75,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,怎么样？好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:06.22,Default,Daughter,0,0,0,,嗯  超好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:10.07,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,孩子他爸  之后要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:13.71,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,喂  孩子他爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:16.48,Default,Daughter,0,0,0,,爸爸  叫你呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.14,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,又发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:21.77,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:24.07,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,你有什么心事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:26.07,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,不  没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:29.73,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,我只是感慨  这样的时间真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:32.02,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,像是谎言一般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:37.23,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,好了  我们接下来去看电影…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:44.97,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:46.82,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:49.64,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,又做噩梦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:52.56,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,抱歉  总是吵醒你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:55.28,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,讲真  去医院看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.55,Default,Daughter,0,0,0,,妈妈  尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:02.64,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,嗯… 你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:05.49,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,好  爸爸和你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.37,Default,Daughter,0,0,0,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:16.57,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,在扫描您先生的电子脑的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:21.32,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,如果您知道可能导致他失眠的因素  请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:24.89,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,他是个非常善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:27.46,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,但他过去好像遭受了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:31.34,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,可能有事情瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:33.33,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,为什么这么觉得？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:38.47,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,这事本来也不该告诉您的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.24,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,那这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:44.72,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,你为什么每个月都向这个账号转钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:47.46,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,而且还是这么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:51.43,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,你是不是被什么人骗了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.10,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,让我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.85,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:57.89,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,以前有个叔叔给了我很多帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:02.36,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,我只是在给他工作的慈善机构捐款
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:05.86,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,这是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:10.00,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,我担心他被卷入了什么麻烦事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.87,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,记忆被篡改?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:18.49,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,嗯  那位患者的记忆在六年前受到篡改
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:23.94,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,很可能是由外部的强制介入改变的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:26.60,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,而且这种做法…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:31.81,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,并非是合法的正规治疗法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:34.08,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,所以才是个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:37.47,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,但是松村完全没有提到过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:39.69,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,他可能忘记了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.48,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,要是调整他电子脑的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:44.40,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,把他接受调整的记忆删除了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.37,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,那也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:49.95,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,调整电子脑的手术  术后护理是必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:53.83,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,如果患者忘记了经历手术这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:05.33,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,这么突然要出门  您是要去哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:07.39,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我去见个老熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:11.72,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,开车要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.69,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.75,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,还特地到我这里来拜访…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:34.31,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,这是什么风把你吹来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:37.07,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,这设备挺不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.66,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,看来你赚了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.29,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,也没那么夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.83,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,先请坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:47.34,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,濑户  是你动了松岛的电子脑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.60,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你这又是来的哪一出啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.42,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:54.68,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,不过我可不能泄露病人的隐私…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.19,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,他应该还在给你转钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:00.33,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不过他本人是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:03.86,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,这是在给「叔叔」的慈善机构捐款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:09.61,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,「叔叔」 我记得你写过相关的论文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:15.97,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,他因为持续多日的失眠和噩梦  前来我的诊所就诊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:17.54,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,那些应该都是副作用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:21.63,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我想知道你采取了什么样的治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:25.17,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,按你的风格  应该都有详细记录的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:29.42,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,我做的治疗  你应该没有猜错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.94,0:07:34.06,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,我在虚拟色情片上花了太多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:37.88,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,还因使用电子毒品惹上了警察
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:42.16,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,每次我都觉得自己完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:45.31,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,但是只要能戒掉酒精  我也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:49.66,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,的确  我能治好你的酒精成瘾症
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:51.89,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,但是松岛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:55.95,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你觉得你戒掉了酒瘾就能幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:02.28,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,如今你缺少改变自己的力量和意志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:04.20,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,如果我就这样治好了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:07.07,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你也会对别的东西成瘾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:10.99,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,我… 到底是哪里有问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.15,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,是我的脑袋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.68,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,松岛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.02,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:20.79,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你的脑袋和身体都没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:24.94,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,有问题的不是你  而是你的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:29.47,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,我的工作就是把它修回正轨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:34.97,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,我将他的电子脑固定成 SOL7 的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.45,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,然后和患者一起回顾过去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:42.07,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,在关键点一处一处地施加诱导  「改良」过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:43.60,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,对于松岛来说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.91,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,只要能创造出他人生的「支柱」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:47.96,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,就自然能重振旗鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:52.34,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你当真有取得他本人的许可吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.39,Default,Seto,0,1000,0,,那是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:58.35,Default,Seto,0,1000,0,,然后终于轮到那个「叔叔」登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:01.80,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,「叔叔」对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:04.40,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,「光是哭泣  什么都改变不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:08.77,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,该发火时就要发火」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.86,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,该发火时…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.01,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,对你施暴的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:16.43,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,还有欺凌你的人  最终都向你道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:19.21,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,就因为你鼓起勇气向他们发火了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:24.20,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,但是  我最后还是没有去上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.38,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,那也是因为「叔叔」的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:32.65,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,「叔叔」教会了你所有重要的人生道理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:37.16,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你记得「叔叔」为你做了什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.39,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,我  不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:43.81,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,让我来帮你回想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:48.73,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,他可是世界上最想让你获得幸福的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:54.98,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你真就是只为了这件事而来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:57.53,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,千万别忘记把数据发给我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.92,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:02.77,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,好啦  你就靠你的方法来抑制他的副作用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:03.88,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,啊对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.16,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,这个  你拿一个回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:10.29,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,繁殖仙人掌可有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.79,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,我给你个袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.98,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,仙人掌是靠扦插来繁殖的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:18.39,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,生命力很强  所以照料起来也省事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:22.89,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,虽这么说  但任何个体缺少了水都会枯死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:25.85,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,弱小的个体就只能放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:32.73,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,所以你就逆转时间给他浇水了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.61,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,浇了充满谎言的水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:37.86,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,那你会如何治疗呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.69,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,光治好他的成瘾症就算是大功告成？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:43.52,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,还是给他安排个精神护理机器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:45.12,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,那样可费时间咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:50.21,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,哪怕是超 AI MICHI 也无法提高成年人的心理韧性哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:54.87,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,对这个患者来说  谎言是能够根治他的特效药
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:57.50,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你也多宽容一下谎言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:01.00,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,能贯彻谎言的技术早就已经存在了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:03.47,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,莫加迪特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.47,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,作为同道中人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.02,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你的事迹我也都有所耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:13.73,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,你也不相信 MICHI 定下的规则是绝对正确
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:17.31,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,所以才会有个暗地里的身份  不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.99,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,医疗没有绝对的正确答案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:30.75,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,在迎来了仿生人这一新成员的世界更是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:35.17,Default,Seto,0,0,0,,真让人为难啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:40.80,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,真的是多谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:44.02,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,多亏了你们  我老公的失眠症也好转了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:45.77,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,我的睡眠不足也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:48.48,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:52.19,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,那个盆栽  我家也有一株
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:54.66,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,是有人送给医生的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:58.99,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,我的好像也是别人送的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.84,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,是谁来着呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:03.59,Default,Daughter,0,0,0,,爸爸  还没好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:05.96,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,嗯  已经搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:08.73,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,那我们先告辞了  医生  多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:10.15,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:11.05,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:11.96,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.12,Default,Daughter,0,0,0,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:13.85,Default,Matsumura,0,0,0,,你想去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:14.82,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,医生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:19.14,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,你不告诉他记忆有被篡改过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:20.52,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,告诉他了又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.48,Default,Daughter,0,0,0,,我想吃冰淇淋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:24.47,Default,Wife,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.97,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,说的… 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:40.89,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,没事的  不要怕  裕太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.99,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,妈妈会陪着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:49.20,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,终于  我被带到医院去就诊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:10.51,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,诶  这是门德尔松么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:12.21,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:14.17,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,真是你弹的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:18.40,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我也想听听你演奏的其他曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:21.02,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,方便的话  下次让我听听看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:26.15,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,好了  诊断结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:31.14,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我和你妈妈谈话时  你去等待室稍等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:38.54,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:42.05,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,可以让诊断架构加入我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.92,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,他是医疗用 AI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:46.42,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,好  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:48.94,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,杰  你能听到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.68,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,我能听到  须堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:53.30,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你有什么看法？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:57.89,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,坦白说  我认为他可以被治疗  也应该接受治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.57,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,如何治疗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:04.95,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,对情绪系统进行调律  是最简单有效的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:08.45,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,对情绪系统… 调律？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:13.70,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,简单来说就是要强行改变裕太的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:17.21,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,你这种说法太粗暴了  须堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.87,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.97,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,让我来解释吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.84,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,以人类为例
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.77,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,人类会因中枢神经的功能障碍等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:30.43,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,各种原因而产生社交障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:35.06,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,如果施以药物疗法或者改善习惯的心理疗法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:37.85,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,基本上都要花费很长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.74,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,但是换成是仿生人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.85,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,就可以直接微调其情绪机制
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:47.56,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,比给人类的药物治疗更加安全  也更有效
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:49.95,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,您有什么疑问吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:55.33,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,有问题可以提出来  我为您解答
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:01.33,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,他真的需要… 这种治疗吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:09.27,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,裕太无法控制住自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:12.23,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,但这可能就是他的个性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:15.35,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,要是这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:21.61,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,这是寻求情绪系统调律的家属中常见的顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.67,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,不过  就数据而言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.23,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,术后对结果不满的例子几乎没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:27.09,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,基于这个情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:28.62,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不用说了  杰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:29.84,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:36.88,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,没有东西落在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:37.82,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:40.42,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,那下周再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:42.23,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,等到那时再回复就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:43.11,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:45.20,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,那我们就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.34,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,喂  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.76,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,下次来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:52.90,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,当真要带其他曲子的录音来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.73,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我之前说的可不是客套话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.06,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,真的是太对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:01.24,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,没关系  不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:03.73,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,等… 等一下  裕太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:09.89,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,她会同意接受治疗吗  他母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:12.85,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,大概会吧  很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:14.49,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,遗憾？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.99,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我喜欢钢琴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:24.23,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,钢琴不会和我吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.14,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,钢琴不会背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.50,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我敲下「哆」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:31.18,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,它一定会以「哆」回应我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:34.58,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,把各种声音排列起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.56,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,在演奏时感觉真是棒极了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:39.60,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,仅仅由我和…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:40.73,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,钢琴组成的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.00,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,裕太  裕太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:48.59,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,裕太  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:49.77,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,该吃晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:52.88,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,但是  我刚刚在录音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:55.16,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,正在状态呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:59.09,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,妈妈不也常常跟你说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:00.97,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,你必须得改变自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:01.87,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.20,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.74,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,为什么妈妈会这样?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:08.33,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,为什么?! 为什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:12.21,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,感觉脑子里被填满了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:15.31,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,全是痛苦的情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:16.82,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,非常难受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:22.73,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我只要有钢琴就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:26.30,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,但是… 其他人会来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:27.48,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,如果他们能消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:31.12,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,如果他们都能消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:32.70,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,一定就能爽快多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.82,Default,Classmate A,0,0,0,,你在瞪什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.20,Default,Classmate A,0,0,0,,有错的人是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:41.73,Default,Classmate B,0,0,0,,我们对你做什么了吗  裕太？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:43.37,Default,Classmate B,0,0,0,,什么都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:45.71,Default,Classmate C,0,0,0,,向小和道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:54.86,Default,Nodoka,0,0,0,,当时我只是问你在听什么曲子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:59.09,Default,Nodoka,0,0,0,,你总是一个人  所以我想交个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:06.45,Default,Nodoka,0,0,0,,结果你突然把我推开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:07.69,Default,Classmate B,0,0,0,,快道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:08.80,Default,Classmate C,0,0,0,,道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:09.73,Default,Classmate A,0,0,0,,道歉  裕太！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:15.62,Default,Classmate B,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:16.78,Default,Classmate C,0,0,0,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:41.05,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,为什么我当时会那么固执呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:44.18,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,事到如今  我也不搞清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:45.85,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:52.01,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,因为在那之后  我接受了治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:58.03,Default,Yuta's Mom,0,0,0,,我的儿子也能交到很多朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:01.52,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,嗯  应该是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:05.29,Default,Yuta Mom,0,0,0,,要知道一直以来  就只有钢琴是他朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:16.82,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:21.30,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,有什么地方不舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.61,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我感觉  没问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:32.02,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,还有  我带来了演奏的录音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:37.37,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,真厉害  全是我喜欢的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.32,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我可以收下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:40.32,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:44.32,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,因为叔叔你夸奖了我的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.60,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,是么  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:54.85,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,从那天以来…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:58.44,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我就变得可以非常冷静地看待自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:04.62,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,也很少有热血上头的情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:12.88,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,也能和班上的同学交好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:32.12,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,裕太  饭做好了  快来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:41.51,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,我现在依旧喜欢钢琴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:49.37,Default,Yuta,0,0,0,,但… 我感觉我弹奏的音色和过去有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.78,Default,Rika,0,0,0,,这钢琴弹得真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:09.65,Default,Rika,0,0,0,,这是什么曲子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:11.71,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,帕蒂塔第一组曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:13.05,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,弹得不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.22,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.72,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,每个音符都感觉绷得很紧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:20.55,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,但让人感觉非常美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:25.67,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,这是之前那个男孩演奏的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:29.08,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不过这是他在接受治疗前的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:35.06,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.07,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,要改变仿生人的性格…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:42.65,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,在技术上并不困难
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:49.07,Default,Female Patient,0,0,0,,我的人生为什么会变成这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:52.49,Default,Seto,0,0,0,flashback,我的工作就是把它修回正轨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:57.12,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,创造虚假的记忆也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.43,0:22:00.18,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:04.63,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,须堂  方便说两句吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:05.64,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.64,0:22:07.70,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,关于裕太的治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:11.21,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,你是否满意我的诊断？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.32,0:22:14.63,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你的工作总是完成得很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:17.65,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不用担心  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.64,0:22:20.01,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,非常感谢
